24
00:06:41,668 --> 00:06:42,888
It's all your fault.

25
00:06:45,834 --> 00:06:47,362
What kind of look is that?

26
00:06:59,394 --> 00:07:02,602
Wu, send me the materials for the case you gave me before.

27
00:07:03,549 --> 00:07:05,256
Who was it that told me before that he was dissatisfied

28
00:07:05,280 --> 00:07:07,447
