35
00:07:55,376 --> 00:07:56,596
Good morning, boss.

36
00:07:57,594 --> 00:07:58,814
Good morning, boss.

37
00:08:00,120 --> 00:08:01,340
Good morning, boss.

38
00:08:03,250 --> 00:08:04,290
Bao Rui.

39
00:08:04,431 --> 00:08:05,662
You look good today.

40
00:08:10,387 --> 00:08:12,537
You're paying more and more attention to me.

41
00:08:13,040 --> 00:08:14,602
That's not good. Be careful.

42
00:08:31,822 --> 00:08:33,453
Boss, let's eat.

43
00:09:25,383 --> 00:09:26,642
Yu Fei, let's go eat.

44
00:09:26,849 --> 00:09:28,787
You can go by yourself. I brought lunch today.

45
00:09:28,937 --> 00:09:30,727
Fei, you can cook?

46
