These are all the dishes I love.

47
00:09:32,752 --> 00:09:34,012
Really?

48
00:09:34,093 --> 00:09:35,790
I can't eat them all. Then, let's eat together.

49
00:09:35,814 --> 00:09:37,034
Okay.

50
00:09:38,920 --> 00:09:40,560
How many pairs of chopsticks do you have?

51
00:09:40,720 --> 00:09:41,940
Two pairs.

52
00:09:43,000 --> 00:09:44,271
Cheng Yao, let's go eat.

53
00:09:44,775 --> 00:09:46,282
I brought my own lunch.

54
00:09:46,582 --> 00:09:47,802
You brought yours too?

55
00:09:48,440 --> 00:09:50,400
Why is everyone bringing their own lunch now?

56
00:09:50,488 --> 00:09:52,002
Let me see, what did you bring?

57
00:09:56,320 --> 00:09:58,042
It looks better than what Yu Fei cooked.

58
00:09:59,433 --> 00:10:01,573
Can you handle eating all of this by yourself?

59
00:10:02,793 --> 00:10:04,974
I accidentally made too much.

60
00:10:05,265 --> 00:10:07,546
- And there's my favorite ribs too. - Cheng Yao, you...

61
00:10:09,280 --> 00:10:10,500
What's wrong?

62
00:10:16,968 --> 00:10:18,599
There's an important document

63
00:10:19,001 --> 00:10:20,441
that I need you to help me retrieve.

64
00:10:21,960 --> 00:10:24,390
Can't we just have the client send it by express delivery?

65
